<task id="task_5E71B81283444DB3882D2E1EBFEE0B64">
  <title>Create a Whole-Page Mbox</title>
  <shortdesc>You can create an mbox that includes the whole page page. 
  </shortdesc>
  <prolog>
    <metadata>
      <othermeta name="solution" content="Target" />
      <othermeta name="topic" content="Advanced" />
    </metadata>
  </prolog>
  <taskbody>
    <steps id="steps_7EC32967B21A43E385FA5395F91DA211">
      <step id="step_9E666E40B4654A20A09B71F7AFCE87EA">
        <cmd>Ensure the page includes a reference to 
			 <filepath>mbox.js</filepath> in the header. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>
            <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;script src="http://www.mycompany.com/​myfolder/mbox.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;​&lt;/script&gt;</codeblock>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_5FF7571E7B624E78BF7118C06F535F82">
        <cmd>Insert 
			 <codeph>mbox default</codeph> and 
			 <codeph>mboxcreate</codeph> functions just inside the page's body
			 tags. 
		  </cmd>
        <stepresult>
          <p>Give the mbox a unique name which makes sense for your campaign
				strategy and company procedures. In the example below, the mbox is named
				myMbox. 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <note>Do not place mbox scripts before the open body tag
				  &lt;body&gt; or after the close body tag 
				  <codeph>&lt;/body&gt;</codeph>. Mboxes depend on the 
				  <codeph>&lt;body&gt; onLoad</codeph> function to execute. 
				</note>
          </p>
          <p>
            <b>Tip:</b> Do not add or remove cells or rows from tables. 
			 </p>
          <p>Example of whole page mbox: 
			 </p>
          <p>
            <table id="table_A609A09826C84800984F96ABF0AF7755">
              <tgroup cols="2">
                <colspec colnum="1" colname="col1" colwidth="*" />
                <colspec colnum="2" colname="col2" colwidth="*" />
                <thead>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">Before 
						</entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">After 
						</entry>
                  </row>
                </thead>
                <tbody>
                  <row>
                    <entry colname="col1">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;head&gt;

&lt;/head&gt;

&lt;body&gt;
&lt;...&gt;
.
.
.
&lt;/...&gt;

&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;

 </codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                    <entry colname="col2">
                      <p>
                        <codeblock outputclass="syntax html">&lt;head&gt;
&lt;script src="/myfolder/mbox.js" type="text/javascript"&gt;
&lt;/script&gt;

&lt;/head&gt;

&lt;body&gt;
&lt;div class="mboxDefault"&gt;
&lt;...&gt;
.
.
.
&lt;/...&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;script type="text/javascript"&gt;
mboxCreate(‘myMbox’);
&lt;/script&gt;
&lt;/body&gt;
&lt;/html&gt;</codeblock>
                      </p>
                    </entry>
                  </row>
                </tbody>
              </tgroup>
            </table>
          </p>
        </stepresult>
      </step>
      <step id="step_CD7E2A5DB6894DA887BFC02DB7034FE3">
        <cmd>
          <xref href="t_Validating_an_Mbox.xml#task_4BB8E090CBBF4C56A39BB63BF1ADB964" type="task" format="dita" scope="local">Validate the mbox</xref>. 
		  </cmd>
      </step>
    </steps>
  </taskbody>
